# Dispatch4You Projects

## Workspace: c:\DispatcherTraining
- Main site: c:\DispatcherTraining\ (HTML/CSS/JS → dispatch4you.com)
- Dispatch Academy: dispatch-academy-app/ (React+Vite+TS+Firebase → /dispatch-academy-app/)
- Map Trainer: map-trainer/ (React+Vite+JS → /map-trainer/)
- Game: adventure/ (React Native + Expo → /game/)

## Deploy
- Branch: main only. Command: git push origin main
- GitHub Actions handles all deploys automatically

## Dispatch Academy
- Firebase project: dispatch4you-80e0f (same as map-trainer)
- State: Zustand + localStorage + Firestore sync
- Styles: Tailwind CSS + framer-motion
- Base path: /dispatch-academy-app/

## Key Rules
- Dispatch fee: 2-4% (NOT 5-10%)
- Broker check: via factoring company MC# (NOT credit score)
- All UI text in Russian
- Dark theme: text #fff/#e2e8f0, accent #06b6d4
- Min font size: 13px
